{"title":"最近最远点对","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":250,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-2319","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>给定平面直角坐标系上的N个点，分别求出距离最近的两个点的距离和距离最远的两个点的距离。注意，距离为直线距离。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行一个整数，N。</p>\n<p>接下来N行每行两个整数，xi,yi，表示第i个点的X坐标与Y坐标。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p align=\"left\">总共一行，两个浮点数，为最短距离与最长距离，保留两位小数。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>4</p>\n<p>0.0 0.0</p>\n<p>0.0 1.0</p>\n<p>1.0 0.0</p>\n<p>1.0 1.0</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>1.00 1.41</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>对于30%的数据，0&lt;N&lt;=2000</p>\n<p>对于70%的数据，0&lt;N&lt;=20000</p>\n<p>对于100%的数据，0&lt;N&lt;=100000，输入数据中所有数不超过10^9。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}